Seq1.ReceiverContent: Okay. Would you like to... Sorry. Go ahead.

Seq3.ReceiverContent: Okay. One moment. Let me check on it. We do have a slot available tomorrow at 10.30 a.m. Will that be okay with you? To meet the doctor in person?

Seq5.CallerContent: That's perfect. Tomorrow at 10.30 is perfect.

Seq6.ReceiverContent: Your last name is Naiman, am I correct?

Seq7.ReceiverContent: Yes. I got you. And may I know the reason of the appointment?

Seq8.ReceiverContent: What did you say? Could you say that again?

Seq9.ReceiverContent: So just to confirm, I have... An appointment tomorrow at 10.30 a.m. to meet the doctor in person.

Seq10.ReceiverContent: Is there anything else that I may ask the students?

Seq11.CallerContent: No. I appreciate your doing this.
Seq11.ReceiverContent: Thank you for calling CrossFit Summer Practice. You have a great day. Bye-bye.
